flowchart TD
    Start[User enters museum] --> Welcome[Welcome overlay]
    Welcome --> Free[Free exploration]
    Welcome --> Guided[Guided tour]
    Free --> Aim[Look at artwork]
    Aim --> Select[Select artwork]
    Guided --> TourStop[Camera moves to artwork stop]
    TourStop --> Select
    Select --> Modal[Artwork modal or media detail]
    Modal --> Close[Close modal]
    Close --> Continue[Continue exploration or tour]
    Continue --> Credits[Credits modal]
    Credits --> End[Session continues or ends]
